name: Sparkling Nectar
description:
This is the second merge I ever mixed; I didn't expect much and didn't document, so the recipe is regrettably lost.


It's really good at making things vibrant and plays really well with particles, mist, all that mystical looking stuff, sometimes trending into it without prompting. Try "particulate," "nebula," "sparkling," etcetera to amp it up.

Clip skip matters a lot. See attached images.
1-3 can all be viable, but it has a quirk where clip skip 1 can break down, possibly correlating with high token count. Higher clip skip also seems to make it less wild.

VAE is baked in. Have fun.
